            window.is_in_ca = false;
            window.is_in_eu = 1;

<script type="text/javascript">

 var token = ''; var currentid = 262604;
  
   function doflag ( assoc_id, type, flag, polarity ) {

      hideflag();
      did('flagimg_' + assoc_id + '_' + type).src = '//web.archive.org/web/20221023034254/https://e.snmc.io/2.5/img/images/loading.gif';
      sendrequest('flagitem|' + token + '|' + assoc_id + '|' + type + '|' + flag + '|' + polarity);
   }


   var flagassocid = 0;
   var flagtype = 's';
   var currentflag = '';

   function flagitem(assoc_id, type, event) { 
      if ( did('flag_' + assoc_id + '_' + type).classname != 'flag0' )
      {
          doflag ( assoc_id, flagtype, '', 0 );
          return;
      }

     var fl = document.getelementbyid('flag');
   
     var pagex, pagey;
   
     if (event.pagex) {
         pagex = event.pagex;
     } else { 
         pagex = event.clientx + document.documentelement.scrollleft;
     }
     if (event.pagey )
     {
         pagey = event.pagey;
     } else {  
         pagey = event.clienty +  document.documentelement.scrolltop;
     }
   
     fl.style.top = pagey + 'px';
     fl.style.left = pagex+ 'px';
     fl.style.visibility='visible';
     flagassocid = assoc_id;
   
   }

   function hideflag() {
    document.getelementbyid('flag').style.visibility='hidden';
   }


 </script>

           window.addeventlistener('load', (event) => {

               for ( var i in window.ryminit ) {
                  var fn = window.ryminit[i];
                  window.ryminit[i] = null;
                  if ( fn ) {
                     fn();
                  }
               }

               window.ryminit = null;
            });

         </script>

               function destroyadhesion(slotname) {
                  console.log(`rym.ads: calling destroyslot on div-gpt-ad-${slotname}`)
                  googletag.destroyslots([window.rym_ad_slot_refs[`div-gpt-ad-${slotname}`]]);
                  let el = document.getelementbyid(`frame-div-gpt-ad-${slotname}`);
                  el.parentnode.removechild(el);
               }

            </script>
